Game Engine (PyGame) NOTE

Main game loop
1. Handle events 
	mouse click and input of the game
	pygame.event.Event objects
2. Update Game state
	logics of the events (win, lose, even), next thing
3. Draw game state to the screen
	animation?

Strategy Enumeration
- Stars and Bars Theorem: To distribute N stars into K bins
- Theorem 2: non-negative: ways to distribute n+k-1 objects to n (or k-1) spots
- itertools.combinations
- the zip() function returns an iterator of tuples based on the iterable object.

